installCask 'duet' duet
installCask 'Horos' Horos
installCask 'Google Earth' google-earth
installCask 'Handbrake' handbrake
installCask 'Firefox' firefox
installCask 'OmniDiskSweeper' omnidisksweeper
installCask 'OmniFocus' omnifocus
